Insider Activity


Individual




Marc Montagner



Mr. Marc Montagner is Chief Financial Officer & Treasurer at Constant Contact, Inc. and Chief Operating Officer & Chief Financial Officer at Endurance International Group Holdings, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Cogent Communications Group, Inc. and Cogent Communications Holdings, Inc. Mr. Montagner was previously employed as Managing Partner by The Dupont Circle Citizens Association, Chief Financial Officer by LightSquared, Inc., Head-Global Telecom, Media & Technology by Banc of America Securities LLC, Head-Corporate Development by France Telecom North America, Inc., a Managing Director by GTT Communications, Inc., Managing Director-Telecom & Media Group by Morgan Stanley, Senior Vice President-Corporate Development by Nextel Communications, Inc., Senior Vice President-Corporate Development by Nextel, Inc., and Senior Vice President-Corporate Development by Sprint Nextel Corp. He received his graduate degree from Télécom ParisTech and an MBA from Columbia University.



